longBusinessSummary: paragon GmbH & Co. KGaA develops, manufactures, and sells electronic components for the automotive industry in Germany, European Union, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Electronics, Mechanics, and Electromobility. The Electronics segment develops and sells sensors, microphones, and instruments primarily for the automotive industry. The Electromobility segment manufactures and sells battery systems and battery management systems for various industries. The Mechanics segment develops and markets lectromechanical components for the automotive and mechanical manufacturing industries.
